io.klerch.alexa.tellask.schema.type

Enum AlexaOutputFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AlexaOutputFormat>
      • io.klerch.alexa.tellask.schema.type.AlexaOutputFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<AlexaOutputFormat>

    public enum AlexaOutputFormat
extends Enum<AlexaOutputFormat>
    The output formats provide a set of SSML pattern. Applied to some value (most likely AlexaSlotSave-fields in state models) it returns a valid SSML which go into a response utterance.
